After that, the student makes a cup of coffee first adding the capsule, and is helped by the instructor because doesn't know how to put it inside the machine. After that, the student removes the capsule from the capsule coffee machine with the instructor's help and places the capsule into the garbage bin. Then, the student attaches back the drip tray. After that, the student detaches again the tray and then pours in the sink the coffee leaked which is in it. Then the student attaches back the drip tray into the capsule coffee machine.
